staging:media: Removed assignments from if statements.

The following coccinelle script found the match:

@simple@
expression E1, E2;
statement S1, S2;
@@

+ E1 = E2;
if (
- (E1 = E2)
+ E1
 )
S1 else S2

@left@
expression E0, E1, E2;
statement S0, S1;
@@
- if ((E1 = E2) < E0)
+ E1 = E2;
+ if (E1 < E0)
S1

